sequenceDiagram
  participant D as Dataset (JSONL)
  participant G as Distillation (OpenRouter)
  participant V as Validation (Pydantic)
  participant S as SFT JSONL
  participant T as Trainer (LoRA SFT)
  participant M as Model

  D->>G: Arabic news stories
  G->>V: JSON candidate outputs
  alt Valid JSON
    V->>S: Write success record
  else Invalid JSON
    V->>S: Write failed record
  end
  S->>T: Load + chat-format + split
  T->>M: Fine-tune + save checkpoint
